i askisi mu paei ws eksis
mia while 1 stin main opu diavazw me tin readline 
spaw ton buffer prwta se ; kai meta | ama spasei se | 
exw pipes ftiaxnw mia for gia kathe simeio pu espase 
kai kalw tin execute pu xriazete . 
mesa stin apli execute psaxnw gia redirections an den brei apla kanei mia mia tis entoles 
stin pipe tsekarw pali gia redirections apla dexomai sto 1o pipe input kai sto last output
otidipote allo apla den to dexete to programma
exw ftiaksei 2-3 sinartiseis gia na spaei o kwdikas
i prwti sinartisi diwxnei ta kena ta perisia
i deuteri dineis enan aplo pinaka xaraktirwn kai enan xaraktira
kai su epistrefei enan disdiastato pinaka spasmeno sto xaraktira pu edwses 
mia sinartisi psaxnei to redirection kai to ti type einai
mia diagrafei ta redirection symbols kai mia sbinei to path kai sto epistrefei ksexwrista gia na to dwseis stin dup2
exw kai merikes xazes sinartiseis gia na allazw xrwma stis printf mu gia na fainete ligo kalitera kathws kai mia pu
tipwnei to arxiko minima.